name: One eye sees the other feels

metadata.name: 𝓒𝓾𝓹𝓲𝓭 <3
metadata.description:
Cupid is a symbol of love for all people. This artwork is of an androgynous Cupid, neither male nor female, but somewhere in between. This mythical character with a body based on the golden ratio depicts intricate details in the piece, conceived with love, inspiration, and high energy! 

𝓒𝓾𝓹𝓲𝓭  💘
Edition: 1/1
2705 x 3448 
Format: PNG
DAIYEGO 2022
@ARTistheutility
